292
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:56,400
Hello.

293
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,592
Hello.

294
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:00,080
Old acquaintances.

295
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,600
Sorry for being late.

296
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,072
Hello.

297
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,480
Hello.

298
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,080
Hello.

299
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,920
- I'll help you carry it over there.
- Thanks.

300
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,240
- Let me carry it for you.
- Do you need help with it?

301
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:17,800
These are gifts for everyone.

302
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:18,880
Thank you, so thoughtful.

303
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:20,080
