- Thanks a lot.

309
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:31,360
Okay.

310
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,600
She has a pretty good personality.

311
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,504
Yes.

312
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,160
