326
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:14,000
What a coincidence.

327
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,560
I am Xu Lvyang.

328
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,560
You can call me Liu.

329
00:16:16,560 --> 00:16:17,472
The Liu from willow.

330
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:18,624
Liu.

331
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:21,240
And my name is Lu Bingkun.

332
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,120
You can call me Lu Bingkun.

333
