334
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,576
To keep it simple.

335
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:26,000
Just call me Dong Zhuoran.

336
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,120
The Zhuo from excellence,
Ran from nature.

337
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,480
Dong Zhuoran.

338
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,480
Just call me Xiaowen.

339
00:16:29,888 --> 00:16:30,760
Xiaowen.

340
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,712
Xiaowen.

341
00:16:33,568 --> 00:16:34,560
Zhou Youling.

342
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:35,560
- Zhou Youling.
- Zhou Youling.

