352
00:16:58,746 --> 00:17:01,428
Ladies, please choose your rooms first.

353
00:17:01,472 --> 00:17:03,776
Then, gentlemen, choose your rooms.

354
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,640
We'll choose the rooms first.

355
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,600
Choose a room first.

356
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:08,360
The girls choose the rooms first.

357
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,880
- Let's go together.
- Let's go.

358
00:17:10,360 --> 00:17:11,280
Together.

359
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:13,080
The balcony of the girls' bedroom.

360
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:14,880
