on the second floor.

364
00:17:19,120 --> 00:17:20,560
Girl, boy, girl, boy.

365
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:21,760
I'll take this one.

366
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,320
Then I'll take this one.

367
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:25,760
Then I'll take this one.

368
00:17:28,128 --> 00:17:29,015
Okay.

369
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,240
Perfect.

370
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,280
