372
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:36,160
Come on.

373
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,160
Which one is my profile picture?
I can't even recognize myself.

374
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,936
Which one is me?

375
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,080
I'm also a little...

376
00:17:45,043 --> 00:17:45,632
(Align properly)

377
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,840
(He's so attentive.)

378
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:51,240
(He helped straighten
the girls' profile pictures.)

379
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,320
She smiled.

380
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:55,560
I'll take a corner suite,

381
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:58,240
Room 211, okay?

382
00:17:59,712 --> 00:18:01,303
(Chen Danqi, Dong Zhuoran)

383
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:03,680
Next to Chen Danqi.

384
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,960
He likes her.

385
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,240
Then I'll lie in the middle.

386
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:15,360
