to be a bit more proactive.

392
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,720
He wants to catch up.

393
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:33,080
Well.

394
00:18:33,472 --> 00:18:34,400
He'll definitely choose the room

395
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,600
