396
00:18:41,230 --> 00:18:43,072
(Xu Lvyang, Jia Peixuan, Zhou Youling)

397
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:47,280
I'll take a room by the side.

398
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,216
- Is that okay?
- Are you okay with it?

399
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,280
You take the side,
and I'll take this one.

400
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,320
Then I'll take this one. Just right.

401
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:53,280
You've already chosen for me.

402
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,760
(It was taken.)

403
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:57,160
(BK was too slow.)

404
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,320
One person, one room.

405
00:18:58,621 --> 00:18:59,560
(Left room, right room)

406
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,800
Then let's go back to our rooms to rest.

407
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:01,792
- Alright?
- Okay.

408
00:19:01,792 --> 00:19:02,912
Alright.

409
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:05,680
