418
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:25,160
- Okay, no problem.
- It's too heavy.

419
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,240
Because I live next to you.

420
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:27,240
Okay. It's very heavy.

421
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,800
I just didn't exercise today.

422
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:31,520
The two of them are somewhat...

423
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,768
Yeah, they seem really
familiar with each other.

424
00:19:32,768 --> 00:19:33,840
Yes.

425
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:35,240
- Give it to me first.
- Thank you.

426
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,120
(Xu Lvyang's suitcase) Zhou Youling voluntarily helps her
with the suitcase.

427
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:39,920
- I'll do it.
- Thanks.

428
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,040
Is yours heavy?

429
00:19:43,104 --> 00:19:44,040
It's heavy.

430
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:45,520
I trust Dong Zhuoran.
Let's wait for him to come down.

431
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,240
I shouldn't overestimate myself.

432
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:49,160
Let's go. Give it to me first.
I'll go up first.

433
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,120
Is it okay? Two suitcases.

434
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:51,072
(Chen Danqi's suitcase, Xu Lvyang's suitcase)
Brother, let's go upstairs.

435
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,160
You've worked hard.

436
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,080
No problem.

437
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,240
I'm going in.

438
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,040
Okay, I'm going inside.

439
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:04,120
There's a story.

440
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:05,856
We're over here.

441
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,680
201.

442
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:14,440
Alright.

443
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:19,960
- This should be yours.
- Okay.

444
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,440
- You don't snore at night, right?
- No, I don't.

445
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,920
I sleep like a log.

446
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,544
His...

447
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:30,920
Why did I

448
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,360
