449
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,480
Hello.

450
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,520
Wait a moment.

451
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:43,440
I put your item at the door.

452
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:45,080
- Okay, thanks.
- You're welcome.

453
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:46,880
(Cute)

454
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:49,568
Chen Danqi.

455
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,080
What a coincidence, I brought this too.

456
00:20:51,280 --> 00:20:52,680
This is really good.

457
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,920
I used to bleach and dye frequently.

458
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,200
My hair was severely damaged.

459
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,320
I relied on it to restore my hair.

460
00:20:56,320 --> 00:20:59,080
It contains skincare-grade
3A peptide essence.

461
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:00,400
It can penetrate deep into the hair core

462
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,880
and reshape the protein structure.

463
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,760
After each use,

464
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,960
my hair becomes smooth and resilient.

465
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,840
I use a different one,

466
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:07,880
rose foam hair mask.

467
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,800
It's also really good.

468
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:10,840
It's ebony rose scented. Smells great.

469
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:12,080
Then I'll try

470
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:13,160
this rose-scented one next time.

471
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,032
Brother, come outside.

472
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:34,400
(I feel quite surprised.)

473
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,800
(Just in such a location)

474
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:37,440
(and such a beautiful environment.)

475
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,480
(The small house
is also decorated warmly.)

476
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:42,680
(Walking inside feels really relaxing.)

477
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:44,520
(Wang Yi, Lu Bingkun)

478
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:45,920
(Everyone has to stay here for a month.)

479
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,280
(Chen Danqi)
There will surely be many interesting stories.

480
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,960
(Dong Zhuoran)
The location

481
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,880
indeed has some advantages.

482
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,360
Of course. The last one
to say good morning,

483
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:54,200
and the last one to say good night...

484
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:56,960
(Xu Lvyang, Zhou Youling, Jia Peixuan, Xiao Wentao)
It's different.

485
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,760
Let's go.

486
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:03,616
Time to eat.

487
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,600
Welcome, everyone,

488
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:18,400
to formally move into the Love House.

489
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,320
During the day, everyone has

490
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:20,520
had a date once,

491
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,880
and each has written down

492
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,080
their initial impressions.

493
00:22:23,360 --> 00:22:25,200
Now everyone can pick up

494
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:27,600
the love messages your date
wrote for you.

495
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:29,160
(Exclusive Note Announcement Rules)
Read the contents of the letters.

496
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:31,080
You can talk freely with one another

497
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:32,680
and make all the guesses you want,
just don't blurt out the answer directly

498
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,920
and don't try to pin each guess
on a specific person.

499
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,640
Only secret inner delight allowed.

500
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:37,600
Likes me. He likes me.

501
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,800
I also like him.

502
00:22:39,104 --> 00:22:40,096
I'll choose...

503
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:43,280
We get to make our picks first,

504
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:44,400
and then read them out loud.

505
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,640
No one knows whose it is.

506
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,760
It should be like this.

507
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:48,440
But for my envelope,

508
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,320
I know how it was sealed.

509
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:50,360
You know? Really?

510
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,160
I haven't looked carefully.

511
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:54,160
Isn't this the time
to test our eyesight?

512
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,320
I really can't tell.

513
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,112
What a feast.

514
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,000
(Record the food)
Take a picture first.

515
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,240
There are also many gifts.

516
00:23:02,496 --> 00:23:03,928
(Meeting gift)

517
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,920
Let's send them later.

518
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,520
He is a very detail-oriented boy.

519
00:23:08,896 --> 00:23:09,880
Bonus points.

520
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:12,240
This makes me seem thoughtless.

521
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,328
What is this?

522
00:23:15,872 --> 00:23:16,840
Each of us

523
00:23:16,840 --> 00:23:17,840
picks an envelope and reads it out loud.

524
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,440
Randomly?

525
00:23:25,216 --> 00:23:26,208
This one.

526
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:30,320
What is this thing? It's so abstract.

527
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:31,648
This one.

528
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:33,800
Then I'll take this one.

529
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:35,744
Let's sit down first.

530
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:37,056
Then I'll sit here.

531
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:44,120
The two of them
ended up sitting together.

532
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:48,000
The atmosphere
is a bit socially awkward

533
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:48,880
