534
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:51,000
Why get socially awkward
reading others' words?

535
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,960
Someone else feels socially awkward.

536
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,360
Someone else? Well, just ignore it.

537
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,856
Who's going to start?

538
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:02,800
See who speaks first.

539
00:24:07,904 --> 00:24:08,864
I'll go first.

540
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,000
To Xuehua Bing.

541
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,120
(Xuehua Bing.)

542
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,880
(Let's see who wrote this
to Xuehua Bing.)

543
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,920
Cherry Blossom Xuehua Bing.

544
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:19,872
And there's a little dog.

545
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:21,720
Cherry Blossom.

546
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,080
Cherry Blossom Xuehua Bing.

547
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,560
Who could it be?

548
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:29,400
(I gave my exclusive note)

549
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,400
(to Zhou Youling.)

550
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,480
(Wang Ze, Zhou Youling)
Just a short sentence.

551
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,600
Cherry Blossom

552
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:34,440
Xuehua Bing.

553
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:36,160
(And I drew)

554
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,600
(a little dog doodle.)

555
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,200
So cute.

556
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,040
Pretty cute.

557
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,000
To Liu.

558
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:49,800
I wonder it's from Xuehua Bing

559
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:50,688
or Bike.

560
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:54,040
(To Liu)
I admire your resilience at work

561
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:56,560
and appreciate how organized you are.

